Adam and SMC are proud to be recognized by this distinguished award program.
July 17th, 2012 - SMC Achieves Responsible Distribution Verification From NACD ...

                        Special Materials Company has earned Responsible Distribution Verification from The National Association of Chemical Distributors (NACD), the benchmark for chemical distributor companies committed to product stewardship and responsible distribution in every phase of chemical storage, handling, transportation, and disposal.
                        With this achievement, Special Material Company now joins an elite group which requires members to continuously improve performance in protecting health, safety, security, and the environment.

