Regional








Corporate
In South-East Asia, SMC is headquartered in Singapore and with well-established regional presence in Malaysia, Vietnam, Indonesia and Philippines.
With our strong foothold in the region, SMC has always been the leader in pneumatic technology, providing industry with technology, innovation and product to support industrial automation based on the guiding principle of “contributing to automation and labour savings in the industry”.



Our Philosophy
At SMC, customer is the prime motivation of our existence. As we serve the automation industries through pneumatics, we strive to provide the latest and most advance products that keep our customers ahead of their competitors.
We shall constantly seek mutually beneficial partnership with our customers, innovation with new products and services and fulfilling our commitments to customer’s satisfaction and out philosophy of
“Always Getting Better”


Quality Policy
SMC Pneumatics (SEA) Pte Ltd
is committed to go forward by bringing together the wisdom of all of SMC’s employees and by having the ideas of Customer First and Quality First as our core business structure.



















   








